{
  "chapter": 285,
  "chapter_summary": "本章围绕徐子陵与侯希白联手营救曹应龙展开。安隆欲对曹应龙施法之际，侯希白借故拖延，独尊堡主解晖突然现身逼问曹应龙下落，安隆被迫应对，侯希白趁机溜走。与此同时，徐子陵在地窖中与莲柔展开激斗，以凌空换气的绝技击退莲柔，成功救出曹应龙，两人在侯希白接应下逃离。三人藏身于侯希白书斋的密室中，曹应龙向徐子陵揭露石之轩的野心与邪道八大高手的内幕，徐子陵赠予鲁妙子面具助其隐姓埋名。侯希白以掩盖追踪香气为由对曹应龙施加手脚，暗藏追踪之意。莲柔的波斯异兽追踪至此，幸得侯希白的香料掩盖气味，巴盟首领丝娜、角罗风等人搜寻无果后离去。章末场景转至寇仲，他决定赴岭南宋家，委托卜天志取出宝图财物用于重建家园，表达了与李世民一决高下的豪情。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_an_long",
      "text": "以隆叔多疑的性格，既知有破莲八着，竟肯不摸个清楚明白，就那么遽然离去，究竟有甚么更紧迫的事呢。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_long",
      "speaker_name": "安隆",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "贤侄像不知个死字是怎么写似的；不过今晚的事确非常古怪，事事出乎料想之外，假如贤侄肯告诉我从何处得到消息，说不定我们可以推诚合作。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_an_long",
      "text": "隆叔不是说笑吧？枉小侄一向对你敬重万分，你却暗里和杨虚彦私通，还妄图谋算石师的爱女。现在竟还说与我合作，实是荒天下之大谬。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_long",
      "speaker_name": "安隆",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "贤侄你确是不知好歹，谁说过要去害石大哥的美丽女儿。你是听谁说的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_hui",
      "speaker_name": "解晖",
      "listener": "char_an_long",
      "text": "曹应龙在那里？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_long",
      "speaker_name": "安隆",
      "listener": "char_jie_hui",
      "text": "我刚才不是交待清楚，曹应龙的任何事，均与我安隆无关吗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_hui",
      "speaker_name": "解晖",
      "listener": "char_an_long",
      "text": "我若非念在一场兄弟情份，便半句话不和你说的立刻出手，在你现在功力损耗的情况下，可保证你捱不了多久。现在肯问你一句，已是非常念旧，安隆你莫要迫我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_long",
      "speaker_name": "安隆",
      "listener": "char_jie_hui",
      "text": "我知二弟对安某人好得没话说，不过此事与三弟有关，更与'邪王'石之轩有直接关系，二弟若因外人而卷入此事，实犯不着。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位前辈既有要事商量，晚辈当然不敢留此叨扰，请啦！",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要走！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "咿唉！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "随我来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "应该没有被人跟踪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "text": "曹当家没事啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "我现在只是个平凡的人，侯公子莫再这么称呼。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我到外面去把风，要溜最好趁今晚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "今次……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "text": "现在最重要的事，就是曹兄如何避开仇家，回去见妻女最后一面，曹兄有甚么打算？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我已失去信心，再不敢有此非份之想。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "text": "若你能脱胎换骨的变作另一个人，改掉走路与言谈举止的习惯，说不定能把心愿完成。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "天下间竟有如此妙品，我包保戴上后连脸肌的微妙变化都可呈现出来，教人绝不怀疑。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "text": "这是由鲁妙子精制的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这便有救哩！但千万别让侯希白知道，别看他现在装出对我漠不关心的样子，但我敢以人头担保，他事后必会找上我，再以毒辣手段追问一切。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "text": "小心点总是好的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "石之轩不但天性邪恶，且野心极大，如苦心孤诣的培养两个徒弟出来，是要完成他两个梦想，即统一江湖和统一魔道，所以侯希白此人大不简单，千万不要轻信他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "text": "既是如此，那石之轩为何要将两个徒弟置于敌对的位置？他们既会自相残杀，更会互相牵制。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "石之轩是个难以测度的人，没多少人能真正明白他，只看他刻意把《不死印卷》留在幽林小谷，而不直接传给两徒，便使人莫明所以。照我看可能连他都难以决定该传给谁？遂任他们争个你死我活，看谁给淘汰出局。魔门中人行事，从不讲人情道义的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "text": "邪道八大高手，除祝玉妍、石之轩、安隆、辟尘、左游仙和尤鸟倦六个人外，另两人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "尚有一个我知晓的，就是东突厥颉利大汗的军师赵德言，此人在魔门内有崇高的地位，被尊称为'魔帅'，魔功高强之极，仅次于祝玉妍和石之轩之下。至于最后一人，身份非常神秘，石之轩曾漏过口风，说此人正潜修一种厉害的功法，却没有说出是谁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "时间无多，我们还要到安隆的旧铺去趁热闹呢。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "两位有否到一丝似有若无的香气，这种香气我尚是第一次遇上，我刚才已有感觉，还以为是曹兄沾上莲柔的香气，但如此持久不散，显然很不对劲，恐怕我们已泄漏行踪。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "幸得侯兄机警，否则会中妖女的手脚。气味该是从头发处发出来的，侯兄有甚么好的提议。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "至少直至刚才那一刻，敌人仍未循气味追来，事实上柔妖女亦不用急；她怎都想不到会恰巧有个像我般对各类香气极有心得的人在旁，故可从容定计。清除香气有多种方法，但由于我们时间紧迫，只要在曹兄的头发略施手脚，保证可把妖女施的香气掩盖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "侯兄请动手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "text": "曹兄若有帽子，我只要沾点在帽外，戴上后可把气味完全掩盖，只要那样走一段路，敌人势将失去追综的凭藉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "text": "我知曹兄对小弟有怀疑之心。但我却可立誓本人绝非乘人之危的卑鄙小人。现在对小弟来说，最重要是不让《不死印卷》落入杨虚彦手内，否则第一个没命的将是小弟。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "它失去线索啦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "我们尚有机会溜走。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们不用走，随我来。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_na",
      "speaker_name": "丝娜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柔公主的波斯狸今趟可能把人追失哩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "真奇怪！竟是巴盟四大首领之一的美姬丝娜。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiao_luo_feng",
      "speaker_name": "角罗风",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要徐子陵仍在巴蜀，定逃不出我们的五指关，盟主许下诺言，不论生死，都要把他送往关中。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_rou",
      "speaker_name": "莲柔",
      "listener": "char_jiao_luo_feng",
      "text": "大公小心一点，徐小子是出名狡猾的人，大公把话说得这么满，若仍给他溜走，旁人会偷笑的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "闻其声如见其人，波斯美女确与别不同。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_na",
      "speaker_name": "丝娜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪！为何小狸追到这里忽然追不下去。这究竟是谁的房子？当是文人雅土之流，若非邻近的人都到灯会去趁热闹，我们可找人问个清楚。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_rou",
      "speaker_name": "莲柔",
      "listener": "char_si_na",
      "text": "算那小子走运吧。留在这里再没有意思，我们走吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "text": "曹兄要我们送你到那里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "speaker_name": "曹应龙",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "只要能到城北的木行街，我有把握可以脱身。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_cao_ying_long",
      "text": "现在最困难是离城，若只在城内，我包保可以办到。",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "接着我们是否到南市安隆的旧铺去碰运气呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "text": "这个当然？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hou_xi_bai",
      "speaker_name": "侯希白",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "子陵确够朋友。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "text": "我都是要往岭南宋家走一趟，志叔给我安排一下，除去沈纶后，我立即动身启程，其他人则返回彭梁去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜天志",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "由志叔陪你走一趟吧。",
      "tone": "关心",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "text": "我另有要事委托志叔去办。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜天志",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "少帅的决定，令我非常感动。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "卜天志",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "少帅今晚为何像心事重重的样子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bu_tian_zhi",
      "text": "我的心情好多了。能有李世民作我的对手，人生还有甚么缺憾？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 285,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 357
    }
